snippet.title: Joseph Anderson
snippet.description: In-depth video game reviews and critiques, with a sharp focus on gameplay and narrative where applicable. The best way to contact me is through email or direct message on Twitter. Youtube notifications come in too regularly for me to reliably see individual comments so if I don't get back to you, try email.
